@startuml
title Observability Correlation Flow
actor User
participant Orchestrator
participant Gateway
participant Executor
participant Tool
participant Collector
participant Backend

User -> Orchestrator : request
Orchestrator -> Gateway : execution request + run ID
Gateway -> Executor : scoped token + trace context
Executor -> Tool : tool call + correlation IDs
Tool -> Collector : telemetry event
Executor -> Collector : span / log / metric
Collector -> Backend : export normalized signals
@enduml
